<h1 id="l:ga2"><font size="4" id="ux-l">Adding item details</font> </h1>     <h2 id="cxqq"> </h2> After saving a MARC record, you are presented with a screen to add item details (or, local holdings). This is where you define the location of the item (home branch), the cost of the item, the barcode, etc. <br /><br /><ul><li>Click 'Add Item' after entering the data for your item</li><li>A confirmation will appear with the item information</li><li>From here you can edit the item or add another item</li></ul>
